<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
  :root { --accent: #fbbf24; --pink: #fb7185; --teal: #5eead4; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { width: 1080px; height: 1440px; overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(900px 700px at 80% 10%, rgba(251,113,133,0.22), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #07091a 100%);
  }
  .frame { position: absolute; inset: 0; padding: 80px 70px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .num { font-size: 32px; letter-spacing: 6px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; }
  h2 { font-size: 78px; line-height: 1.2; font-weight: 900; margin: 14px 0 0; color: #fff; }

  .center { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; }
  .vs {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 28px; margin: 30px 0;
  }
  .card {
    border-radius: 28px; padding: 40px 32px; min-height: 360px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  }
  .card.bad {
    background: rgba(251,113,133,0.08);
    border: 3px solid rgba(251,113,133,0.4);
  }
  .card.good {
    background: rgba(94,234,212,0.08);
    border: 3px solid rgba(94,234,212,0.4);
  }
  .card .lbl { font-size: 30px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .card.bad .lbl { color: var(--pink); }
  .card.good .lbl { color: var(--teal); }
  .card .big { font-size: 120px; font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -2px; }
  .card.bad .big { color: var(--pink); text-decoration: line-through; text-decoration-thickness: 5px; opacity: 0.85; }
  .card.good .big { color: var(--accent); }
  .card .unit { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 700; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); margin-top: 12px; }
  .card .note { font-size: 26px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5); margin-top: 16px; line-height: 1.5; }

  .verdict {
    margin-top: 22px; padding: 32px 38px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(251,191,36,0.12), rgba(94,234,212,0.06));
    border-left: 6px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 16px;
    font-size: 38px; line-height: 1.55; color: #fff; font-weight: 700;
  }
  .verdict em { font-style: normal; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; }

  .arrow {
    text-align: center; font-size: 70px; color: var(--accent);
    margin: 0 -20px;
  }

  .foot { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-align: right; font-weight: 600; }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="frame">
  <div class="num">PAIN POINT · 02</div>
  <h2>痛点：一个人对<br>56 个项目<br>无解</h2>
  <div class="center">
    <div class="vs">
      <div class="card bad">
        <div class="lbl">❌ 传统</div>
        <div class="big">28</div>
        <div class="unit">小时</div>
        <div class="note">每个项目 30 分钟<br>×56 个 = 一天半</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card good">
        <div class="lbl">✅ AI 并行</div>
        <div class="big">30</div>
        <div class="unit">分钟</div>
        <div class="note">7 个 sub-agent<br>同时跑 = 8 项目/人</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="verdict">
      把 <em>串行</em> 改成 <em>并行</em><br>
      就是这一晚的核心解法
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="foot">SLIDE 02 / 05</div>
</div>
</body></html>
